for this town.

12:31.054 --> 12:32.969
Now watch this backflip.

12:39.410 --> 12:40.803
Mayor Jareb Parker,

12:40.847 --> 12:43.371
a kid who would tell me
everything

12:43.414 --> 12:45.634
if only he knew...
anything.

12:49.856 --> 12:54.251
[ Camera shutter clicking ]

12:54.295 --> 12:56.340
[ Car door closes ]

12:56.384 --> 12:59.300
The girl -- Delilah -- I feel
like she's up to something,

12:59.343 --> 13:01.302
