Nate Parker.

13:07.874 --> 13:10.311
I probably didn't need
to make a list of four people,

13:10.354 --> 13:13.270
but I'm very visual.

13:13.314 --> 13:15.403
Why the hell is milk
$10 a gallon?

13:15.446 --> 13:17.231
