about it?

13:18.580 --> 13:19.886
I mean,
I'm just a flipping mayor.

13:19.929 --> 13:21.148
Okay, well, the
mayor's gonna have to

13:21.191 --> 13:22.627
eat his cereal with water

13:22.671 --> 13:23.672
