13:44.214 --> 13:45.737
Are we doing this?

13:45.781 --> 13:47.783
Yes.
Okay. Yeah.
All right, sure, man.

13:47.827 --> 13:50.568
[ Grunts ]
Good. A handshake, too. Okay.

13:50.612 --> 13:52.744
-Doodle-oodle-oodle-oodle-oodle.
-That's long enough.

13:52.788 --> 13:54.659
Pssch! Unh!

13:54.703 --> 13:57.010
Nice to meet you, fam!
What up?

13:57.053 --> 13:58.794
Not much...at all.

13:58.838 --> 14:01.362
Yo, I'm looking at this
little fool, and he be like,

14:01.405 --> 14:03.886
"Er, I'm not so sure
about this little brown boy."

14:03.930 --> 14:06.367
I never said that.
[ Chuckles ]

14:06.410 --> 14:07.977
You seem like a nice,
stand-up kid.

14:08.021 --> 14:09.631
He is.
That's exactly what he is.

14:09.674 --> 14:10.980
I know.
That's why I said it.

14:11.024 --> 14:13.287
Yo, you don't got
to worry about me none.

14:13.330 --> 14:15.028
I don't drink.
I don't do drugs.

14:15.071 --> 14:18.118
