makes me trust you less.

14:19.684 --> 14:22.731
[ Laughs hysterically ]

14:22.774 --> 14:23.950
Oh, man.

14:23.993 --> 14:26.517
Hey, speaking of
a stand-up guy,

14:26.561 --> 14:28.563
I got a one-man comedy
flow I'm gonna do.

14:28.606 --> 14:30.304
You should pop by
and check out my game.

14:30.347 --> 14:32.349
Yeah. Yeah, okay.
