14:32.393 --> 14:33.785
You better,
or you're a racist.

14:35.352 --> 14:39.139
[ Laughs ]
Oh, God!

14:39.182 --> 14:40.923
J-play. J.K.

14:40.967 --> 14:42.751
J-play all day.

14:42.794 --> 14:45.667
D, let's bounce.

14:47.103 --> 14:50.628
Holy shit.
What the hell was that?

14:50.672 --> 14:52.065
That's the guy you like?

14:52.108 --> 14:55.982
Mm-hmm, but mostly I'm just
using him for his car.

14:56.025 --> 14:57.984
I'll let you use our car.

14:59.768 --> 15:01.291
[ Objects clatter ]

15:01.335 --> 15:03.424
Stop flipping!

15:03.467 --> 15:06.383
♪♪

15:06.427 --> 15:08.646
-Hey.
-Sorry I'm late. Did I miss it?

15:08.690 --> 15:11.345
No, you didn't. Apparently
it's dope to start an hour late.

15:11.388 --> 15:13.129
-Is that him?
-That is him.

15:13.173 --> 15:15.915
-Yeah!
-Oh. Oh! That's -- That's fancy.

15:15.958 --> 15:17.481
Did you sign off
on this guy?

15:17.525 --> 15:19.396
Yeah. I had no choice.
She likes him.

15:19.440 --> 15:21.181
He's harmless.

15:21.224 --> 15:22.530
How many 16-year-olds

15:22.573 --> 15:24.184
have enough material
for a one-man show?

15:24.227 --> 15:25.533
What is he gonna talk about

15:25.576 --> 15:27.317
besides video games
and jerking off?

15:27.361 --> 15:29.667
Our son is the mayor.
Kids are capable of things.

15:29.711 --> 15:31.060
That was an accident.

15:31.104 --> 15:34.890
Yo, yo, yo, yo, yo, yo!
Show some love!

15:34.934 --> 15:36.979
Make some noise![ Applause ]

15:37.023 --> 15:41.201
Give it up for "Massan"!

15:41.244 --> 15:42.550
I thought you said
his name was Mason.

15:42.593 --> 15:43.943
That's how
he introduced himself to me.

15:43.986 --> 15:47.424
-Shh.
-Yeah! What up?

15:47.468 --> 15:49.339
All right, everybody, listen up.
Listen up.

15:49.383 --> 15:51.907
I met the girl of my dreams.

15:51.951 --> 15:53.822
[ Audience awws ]

15:53.865 --> 15:56.564
It was like when Kanye met Kim,
when Jay met Bey,

15:56.607 --> 15:58.827
when Luke met Leia...
before they knew.

15:58.870 --> 16:01.003
[ Laughter ][ Chuckles ]

16:01.047 --> 16:03.875
It's a half-joke.Shh! It's very funny.

16:03.919 --> 16:06.008
Is it?
It's funny
because it's important,

16:06.052 --> 16:09.142
and it's important
because it's diverse.

16:09.185 --> 16:10.534
Then why
aren't you laughing?

16:10.578 --> 16:13.276
So, check this.
Friday night, date night.

16:13.320 --> 16:16.540
[ Laughs loudly ]
So important.

16:16.584 --> 16:17.889
Nobody's buying that.

16:17.933 --> 16:21.458
So, I jump on my bike,
and I ride over.

16:21.502 --> 16:24.331
And I'm ridin' solo --
not Han.

16:24.374 --> 16:26.028
I'm talking Derulo.

16:26.072 --> 16:27.421
Does he have
a recumbent bike?

16:27.464 --> 16:29.292
No. He's got a Miata.
I've got a bike.

16:29.336 --> 16:31.425
And I meet her dad.

16:31.468 --> 16:33.731
And he gives me thatlook...

16:33.775 --> 16:36.473
[ Audience groaning ]...that look
all immigrant kids get

16:36.517 --> 16:39.520
when all they're searching for
is a simple handshake and hello.

16:39.563 --> 16:41.478
That's exactly what I did.
