Islamabad United 93 9/11!

17:03.326 --> 17:04.675
[ Audience groaning ]

17:04.719 --> 17:06.242
I never said that.
Who would say that?

17:06.286 --> 17:07.809
Nobody,
because it's not a sentence.

17:07.852 --> 17:09.941
-So insulting.
-But I'm not stoop to his level

17:09.985 --> 17:11.943
because when he goes low,
I go fly.

17:11.987 --> 17:13.554
[ Laughter ]That's right.

17:13.597 --> 17:15.643
So, I said, "I really care
