18:01.036 --> 18:02.603
You all know
this kid is lying.

18:02.646 --> 18:03.995
Delilah, speak.

18:07.608 --> 18:09.827
Delilah, now!

18:09.871 --> 18:13.701
Okay, okay,
I guess I should say something.

18:13.744 --> 18:18.706
I, um -- I think I should just
maybe formally apologize to you,

18:18.749 --> 18:22.971
