18:26.714 --> 18:28.498
She likes him.
What am I gonna do?Well, she shouldn't.

18:28.542 --> 18:30.674
I know she shouldn't,
but she does, okay,

18:30.718 --> 18:31.719
and I don't want
to push her away.

18:31.762 --> 18:33.460
Ha. No, no, no.

18:33.503 --> 18:36.115
That's not enough.
Is it, folks?

18:36.158 --> 18:37.377
Audience: No!

18:37.420 --> 18:39.727
No, because he called
you "Tora Bora."

18:39.770 --> 18:42.033
[ Audience murmuring ]

18:42.077 --> 18:45.254
I didn't, but okay.
All right.

18:45.298 --> 18:47.474
[ Inhales sharply ]
You're right, you know?

18:47.517 --> 18:49.171
We -- We, uh -- We can do
better. I can do better.

18:49.215 --> 18:51.042
We can all do better,
right?

18:51.086 --> 18:55.308
And, uh, Mason -- Massan, next
time you drive over to my house

18:55.351 --> 18:58.180
on your bicycle,

18:58.224 --> 19:00.008
