in Afghanistan.

19:02.315 --> 19:03.925
-Oh, my God, you --
-Shh.

19:03.968 --> 19:07.320
Look at that.

19:07.363 --> 19:13.021
Boom goes the dynamite![ Hip-hop music plays ]

